Package myVelibRides

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PlanningRide
    This abstract class is like the strategy interface in the strategy design pattern
    PlanningRideAvoidPlus
    In this class we override the method plan that looks for the optimal departure and arrival stations in case the user wants to avoid the plus stations as arrival stations
    PlanningRideFastestPath
    In this class, we override the plan method so that it returns the departure and arrival stations that will allow to have the fastest path
    PlanningRidePreferPlus
    In this class, we override the plan method so that one tries to have a plus station as a destination.
    PlanningRideShortestPath
    In this class, we override the plan method so that it returns the departure and arrival stations that will allow to have the shortest path.
    PlanningRideUniformityPreservation
    In this class, we override the plan method of PlanningRide for the case the user wants to preserve the uniformity of bicycles repartition inside the stations.
    Ride
    This class describes a ride between two stations of the myvelib network
